summary: Riverwood Enhancements. Added light sources, plants, fish and a fire pit!
descriptionHtml:
Riverwood Enhancements. Added light sources, plants, fish and a fire pit!
See video at: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzPabx39fUg&feature=youtu.be

This is my first mod ever and am not sure if I will continue to mod or update. It will all depend on the response I get from this one. If you like, please ENDORSE!

Should be compatible with most mods; as long as they do not modify the same cells. This mod has been built around WATER (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13268) so it will be compatible.

Need to give credit to Sharpshooter for his ENB Mod ( http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=15105); which is seen in the video.

Last but not least, I got a lot of my inspiration from: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13734
Due to mod conflicts, I decided to start from scratch and create my own.
author: Steamin
